OL,3,CDiocese 'ashamed' after allegations
OL,4,Cagainst deceased priest 'credible'
OL,6,FIn a joint statement The Bishop of
OL,7,FDover, Rt Revd Rose Hudson-Wilkin, and
OL,8,Fthe Dean of Canterbury, The Very
OL,9,FReverend Dr David Monteith, said they
OL,10,Fconsider these allegations to be
OL,11,F"credible on the balance of
OL,12,Fprobability".
OL,14,FIn a statement they said: "We are
OL,15,Fsaddened and ashamed that this has
OL,16,Fhappened at the Cathedral and Diocese
OL,17,Fwith our duty of care and
OL,18,Fresponsibility to those in our charge.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
