OL,3,CDiocese 'ashamed' after allegations
OL,4,Cagainst deceased priest 'credible'
OL,6,F"To that end, this case has been
OL,7,Freferred to our Interim Diocesan and
OL,8,FCathedral Safeguarding Advisory Panel
OL,9,FChair, Dr Liza Thompson, to consider
OL,10,Fwhether the threshold for a
OL,11,FSafeguarding Practice Review has been
OL,12,Fmet."
OL,14,F"As representatives of the Cathedral
OL,15,Fand Diocese, we apologise unreservedly
OL,16,Fto the survivors and victims, those
OL,17,Fwho have come forward, all those in
OL,18,Ftheir cohort at the time, and to all
OL,19,Fothers affected.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
