OL,3,CDiocese 'ashamed' after allegations
OL,4,Cagainst deceased priest 'credible'
OL,6,F"We acknowledge the wrong and the harm
OL,7,Fexperienced by the survivors and
OL,8,Fvictims, and the ongoing impact this
OL,9,Fhas had on survivors. We are truly
OL,10,Fsorry."
OL,12,FA complaint was also made regarding a
OL,13,Fplaque in memory of David Marriott at
OL,14,FWye Church.
OL,16,FFollowing a meeting on 15 July, the
OL,17,FParochial Church Council resolved to
OL,18,Fsupport an application to remove the
OL,19,Fplaque.
