OL,3,CDiocese 'ashamed' after allegations
OL,4,Cagainst deceased priest 'credible'
OL,6,FThe Diocese says the relatives of
OL,7,FDavid Marriott were also informed of
OL,8,Fthe allegations, and offered support.
OL,10,FThe statement continued: "Today, the
OL,11,FCathedral and Diocese have robust
OL,12,Fsafeguarding measures in place to
OL,13,Fprotect children and vulnerable adults.
OL,15,F"We have a duty of care and
OL,16,Fresponsibility which is an extremely
OL,17,Fserious trust, and one of our most
OL,18,Fimportant concerns."
